item.title: Things to Look Forward To
item.description: Let me tell you, September is not going well for me. I’m having some - mostly emotional - issues thanks to either myself or some external circumstances. It’s nothing huge really I’m just tired of not being able to do what I want as things go sideways when I’m thinking I’m on track. Anyway, there’s quite a few things that are either happening now or going to happen - well, or at least I hope so.
